observations.recommendation:
1. Prepare and implement a Solid Waste Management Plan as provided under R.A. 9003 and submit the same to the auditor concerned;
2. Formulate a detailed procedures and guidelines to implement the SWM System; and
3. Information and education campaign to reduce if not prevent illegal disposal of the garbage.

